passive.description:
After casting 4 spells, Annie's next offensive spell will stun the target.

Annie begins the game and respawns with Pyromania available.
passive.name: Pyromania

spells.description: Annie hurls a Mana infused fireball, dealing damage and refunding the Mana cost if it destroys the target.
spells.name: Disintegrate

spells.description: Annie casts a blazing cone of fire, dealing damage to all enemies in the area.
spells.name: Incinerate

spells.description: Grants Annie or an ally a shield, a burst of Move Speed, and damages enemies who strike her with attacks or spells.
spells.name: Molten Shield

spells.description: Annie wills her bear Tibbers to life, dealing damage to units in the area. Tibbers can attack and also burns enemies that stand near him.
spells.name: Summon: Tibbers

passive.description: Olaf gains Attack Speed and Life Steal based on his missing Health.
passive.name: Berserker Rage

spells.description: Olaf throws an axe into the ground at a target location, dealing damage to enemies it passes through and reducing their Armor and Move Speed. If Olaf picks up the axe, the ability's cooldown is reset.
spells.name: Undertow

spells.description: Olaf's Attack Speed is increased, he reduces incoming damage, and he gains a Shield.
spells.name: Tough It Out

spells.description: Olaf attacks with such force that it deals true damage to his target and himself, refunding the Health cost if he destroys the target.
spells.name: Reckless Swing

spells.description: Olaf passively gains increased armor and magic resist. He can activate this ability to become immune to disables for as long as he keeps attacking.
spells.name: Ragnarok

passive.description: Every few seconds, Galio's next basic attack deals bonus magic damage in an area.
passive.name: Colossal Smash

spells.description: Galio fires two windblasts that converge into a large tornado that deals damage over time.
spells.name: Winds of War

spells.description: Galio charges a defensive stance, moving slowly. Upon releasing the charge, Galio will taunt and damage nearby enemies.
spells.name: Shield of Durand

spells.description: Galio will briefly step back and charge, knocking up the first enemy champion he encounters.
spells.name: Justice Punch

spells.description: Galio designates an ally's position as his landing spot, granting all allies in the area a magic shield. After a delay Galio smashes down location, knocking up nearby enemies.
spells.name: Hero's Entrance

passive.description: Upon killing a unit, Twisted Fate rolls his 'lucky' dice receiving 1 to 6 bonus gold.
passive.name: Loaded Dice

spells.description: Twisted Fate throws three cards, dealing damage to each enemy unit they pass through.
spells.name: Wild Cards

spells.description: Twisted Fate chooses a magic card from his deck, and uses that for his next attack, causing bonus effects.
spells.name: Pick a Card

spells.description: Every 4 attacks, Twisted Fate deals bonus damage. In addition, his Attack Speed is increased.
spells.name: Stacked Deck

spells.description: Twisted Fate predicts the fortunes of his foes, revealing all enemy champions and enabling the use of Gate, which teleports Twisted Fate to any target location in 1.5 seconds.
spells.name: Destiny

passive.description: Every third attack deals bonus damage and heals Xin Zhao.
passive.name: Determination

spells.description: Xin Zhao's next 3 standard attacks deal increased damage with the third attack knocking an opponent into the air.
spells.name: Three Talon Strike

spells.description: Xin Zhao slashes in front of himself with his spear, then thrusts it forward, slowing affected enemies and marking them as Challenged.
spells.name: Wind Becomes Lightning

spells.description: Xin Zhao charges to an enemy, gaining increased Attack Speed and dealing damage to all enemies in the area, slowing them briefly. Audacious Charge gains increased range against Challenged targets.
spells.name: Audacious Charge

spells.description: Xin Zhao challenges an enemy he damaged recently. Xin Zhao deals damage to nearby enemies based on their current Health and knocks non-challenged targets back, becoming impervious to damage dealt by champions outside of the circle created.
spells.name: Crescent Guard

passive.description: Urgot's basic attacks and Purge periodically trigger blasts of flame from his legs, dealing physical damage.
passive.name: Echoing Flames

spells.description: Fires an explosive charge at the target location, dealing physical damage and slowing enemies caught in the explosion.
spells.name: Corrosive Charge

spells.description: Urgot slows himself while he unloads his weapon on nearby enemies. Prioritizes enemy champions Urgot has recently struck with other abilities and triggers Echoing Flames.
spells.name: Purge

spells.description: Urgot charges in a direction, shielding himself and trampling non-champion enemies. If he catches an enemy champion, he will stop and hurl them out of his way.
spells.name: Disdain

spells.description: Urgot fires a chem-drill that impales the first enemy champion hit. If that champion falls below a health threshold, Urgot judges them weak and can execute them.
spells.name: Fear Beyond Death

passive.description: When LeBlanc drops below 40% Health, she becomes invisible for 1 second and creates a Mirror Image that deals no damage and lasts for up to 8 seconds.
passive.name: Mirror Image

spells.description: LeBlanc projects a sigil, dealing damage and marking the target for 3.5 seconds. Damaging the marked target with an ability detonates the sigil, dealing additional damage.
spells.name: Sigil of Malice

spells.description: LeBlanc dashes to a location, dealing damage to enemies near her destination. For the next 4 seconds, activate Distortion again to return LeBlanc to her starting location.
spells.name: Distortion

spells.description: LeBlanc launches a chain that shackles the first enemy hit. If the target remains shackled for 1.5 seconds, LeBlanc roots them and deals additional damage.
spells.name: Ethereal Chains

spells.description: LeBlanc casts a mimicked version of one of her basic spells.
spells.name: Mimic

passive.description: Every 30 points of bonus Health gives Vladimir 1 Ability Power and every 1 point of Ability Power gives Vladimir 1.6 bonus Health (does not stack with itself).
passive.name: Crimson Pact

spells.description: Vladimir steals life from the target enemy. When Vladimir's resource is full, Transfusion will benefit from massively increased damage and healing for a brief time.
spells.name: Transfusion

spells.description: Vladimir sinks into a pool of blood, becoming untargetable for 2 seconds. Additionally, enemies on the pool are slowed and Vladimir siphons life from them.
spells.name: Sanguine Pool

spells.description: Vladimir pays his own health to charge up a reservoir of blood which, when released, deals damage in the area around him but can be blocked by enemy units.
spells.name: Tides of Blood

spells.description: Vladimir infects an area with a virulent plague. Affected enemies take increased damage for the duration. After a few seconds, Hemoplague deals magic damage to infected enemies and heals Vladimir for each enemy Champion hit.
spells.name: Hemoplague

passive.description: Fiddlesticks' trinket is replaced by scarecrow effigies.
passive.name: A Harmless Scarecrow

spells.description: Fiddlesticks damaging enemies with spells while unseen or targeting an enemy with Terrify's activation strikes a target unit with fear, causing it to flee in terror for a duration.
spells.name: Terrify

spells.description: Fiddlesticks drains health from nearby enemies, dealing bonus execute damage at the end of the duration.
spells.name: Bountiful Harvest

spells.description: Fiddlesticks slashes an area with its scythe, slowing all enemies hit and silencing enemies hit in the center of the slash.
spells.name: Reap

spells.description: A murder of crows flock wildly around Fiddlesticks, dealing damage per second to all enemy units in the area.
spells.name: Crowstorm

passive.description: Kayle's attacks are empowered by the heavens as she levels up and spends skill points. Her wings are lit aflame as she progressively gains Attack Speed, Move Speed, Attack Range, and waves of fire on her attacks.
passive.name: Divine Ascent

spells.description: Kayle conjures a portal, summoning a celestial sword that pierces through enemies, slowing, damaging, and reducing the resistances of all hit.
spells.name: Radiant Blast

spells.description: Blessed by the divine, Kayle heals and grants Move Speed to herself and the nearest ally.
spells.name: Celestial Blessing

spells.description:
Passive: Kayle's celestial sword, Virtue, deals bonus magic damage to enemies she attacks.

Active: Kayle's next attack smites her target with celestial fire, dealing bonus damage proportionate to their missing health.
spells.name: Starfire Spellblade

spells.description: Kayle makes an ally invulnerable and calls upon former Aspects of Justice to purify the area around her target with a holy rain of swords.
spells.name: Divine Judgment

passive.description: Every few consecutive basic attack, Master Yi strikes twice.
passive.name: Double Strike

spells.description: Master Yi teleports across the battlefield with blinding speed, dealing physical damage to multiple units in his path, while simultaneously becoming untargetable. Alpha Strike can critically strike and deals bonus physical damage to monsters. Basic attacks reduce Alpha Strike's cooldown.
spells.name: Alpha Strike

spells.description: Master Yi rejuvenates his body by focus of mind, restoring Health and taking reduced damage for a short time. In addition, Master Yi will gain stacks of Double Strike and pause the remaining duration on Wuju Style and Highlander for each second he channels.
spells.name: Meditate

spells.description: Grants bonus true damage on basic attacks.
spells.name: Wuju Style

spells.description: Master Yi moves with unparalleled agility, temporarily increasing his Move Speed and Attack Speed as well as making him immune to all slowing effects. While active, Champion kills or assists extend Highlander's duration. Passively reduces cooldown for his other abilities on a kill or assist.
spells.name: Highlander

passive.description: Alistar charges his roar by stunning or displacing enemy champions or when nearby enemies die. When fully charged he heals himself all nearby allied champions.
passive.name: Triumphant Roar

spells.description: Alistar smashes the ground, dealing damage to nearby enemies and tossing them into the air.
spells.name: Pulverize

spells.description: Alistar rams a target with his head, dealing damage and knocking the target back.
spells.name: Headbutt

spells.description: Alistar tramples nearby enemy units, ignoring unit collision and gaining stacks if he damages an enemy champion. At full stacks Alistar's next basic attack against an enemy champion deals additional magic damage and stuns them.
spells.name: Trample

spells.description: Alistar lets out a wild roar, removing all crowd control effects on himself, and reducing incoming physical and magical damage for the duration.
spells.name: Unbreakable Will

passive.description: <mainText>Ryze's spells deal extra damage based on his Bonus Mana, and he gains a percentage increase to his maximum Mana based on his Ability Power.</mainText>
passive.name: Arcane Mastery

spells.description:
Passively, Ryze's other basic abilities reset the cooldown of Overload and charge a rune. When Ryze casts Overload with 2 runes charged, he gains a brief burst of Move Speed.

On cast, Ryze throws a charge of pure energy in a line, dealing damage to the first enemy struck. If the target has Flux on it, Overload deals extra damage and bounces to nearby enemies with Flux.
spells.name: Overload

spells.description: Ryze traps a target in a cage of runes, damaging them and slowing their movement. If the target has Flux on it, they are instead rooted.
spells.name: Rune Prison

spells.description: Ryze releases an orb of pure magical power that damages an enemy and debuffs all nearby enemies. Ryze's spells have additional effects against the debuffed enemy.
spells.name: Spell Flux

spells.description:
Passively, Overload deals even more damage against targets with Flux.

On cast, Ryze creates a portal to a nearby location. After a few seconds, allies standing near the portal are teleported to the target location.
spells.name: Realm Warp

passive.description: After being killed, Sion will temporarily reanimate with rapidly decaying Health. His attacks become very rapid, heal him, and deal bonus damage based on his target's maximum Health.
passive.name: Glory in Death

spells.description: Sion charges a powerful swing in an area in front of himself that will deal damage to enemies when released. If he charges for enough time, enemies hit by the swing will also be knocked up and stunned.
spells.name: Decimating Smash

spells.description: Sion shields himself and can reactivate after 3 seconds to deal Magic Damage to enemies nearby. When Sion kills enemies, he passively gains maximum Health.
spells.name: Soul Furnace

spells.description: Sion fires a short range shockwave that damages and slows and reduces the Armor of the first enemy hit. If the shockwave hits a minion or monster, it will be knocked back, damaging, slowing, and reducing the Armor of all enemies that it passes through.
spells.name: Roar of the Slayer

spells.description: Sion charges in a direction, ramping up speed over time. He can steer his charge slightly with the mouse cursor location. When he collides with an enemy he deals damage and knocks them up based on the distance he has charged.
spells.name: Unstoppable Onslaught

passive.description: Sivir gains a short burst of Move Speed when she attacks an enemy champion.
passive.name: Fleet of Foot

spells.description: Sivir hurls her crossblade like a boomerang, dealing damage each way.
spells.name: Boomerang Blade

spells.description: Sivir's next few basic attacks gain additional attack speed and bounce to nearby targets, dealing reduced damage while bouncing.
spells.name: Ricochet

spells.description: Creates a magical barrier that blocks a single enemy ability cast on Sivir. She receives health and a burst of movement speed if a spell is blocked.
spells.name: Spell Shield

spells.description: Sivir leads her allies in battle, granting them a surge of Move Speed for a period of time. In addition, Sivir's attacks reduce her spell cooldowns.
spells.name: On The Hunt

passive.description: Soraka runs faster towards nearby low health allies.
passive.name: Salvation

spells.description: A star falls from the sky at the target location dealing magic damage and slowing enemies. If an enemy champion is hit by Starcall, Soraka recovers Health.
spells.name: Starcall

spells.description: Soraka sacrifices a portion of her own health to heal another friendly champion.
spells.name: Astral Infusion

spells.description: Creates a zone at a location that silences all enemies inside. When the zone expires, all enemies still inside are rooted.
spells.name: Equinox

spells.description: Soraka fills her allies with hope, instantly restoring health to herself and all allied champions.
spells.name: Wish

passive.description: If Teemo stands still and takes no actions for a short duration, he becomes Invisible indefinitely. If he's in brush, Teemo can enter and maintain his Invisibility while moving. After leaving Invisibility, Teemo gains the Element of Surprise, increasing his Attack Speed for a few seconds.
passive.name: Guerrilla Warfare

spells.description: Obscures an enemy's vision with a powerful venom, dealing damage to the target unit and blinding it for the duration.
spells.name: Blinding Dart

spells.description: Teemo scampers around, passively increasing his Move Speed until he is struck by an enemy champion or turret. Teemo can sprint to gain bonus Move Speed that isn't stopped by being struck for a short time.
spells.name: Move Quick

spells.description: Each of Teemo's attacks will poison the target, dealing damage on impact and each second after for 4 seconds.
spells.name: Toxic Shot

spells.description: Teemo throws an explosive poisonous trap using one of the mushrooms stored in his pack. If an enemy steps on the trap, it will release a poisonous cloud, slowing enemies and damaging them over time. If Teemo throws a mushroom onto another mushroom it will bounce, gaining additional range.
spells.name: Noxious Trap

passive.description: Increases Tristana's Attack Range as she levels.
passive.name: Draw a Bead

spells.description: Tristana fires her weapon rapidly, increasing her Attack Speed for a short time.
spells.name: Rapid Fire

spells.description: Tristana fires at the ground to propel her to a distant location, dealing damage and slowing surrounding units for a brief period where she lands.
spells.name: Rocket Jump

spells.description: When Tristana kills a unit, her cannonballs burst into shrapnel, dealing damage to surrounding enemies. Can be activated to place a bomb on a target enemy that explodes after a short duration dealing damage to surrounding units.
spells.name: Explosive Charge

spells.description: Tristana loads a massive cannonball into her weapon and fires it at an enemy unit. This deals Magic Damage and knocks the target back. If the target is carrying the Explosive Charge bomb, the bomb detonation radius is doubled.
spells.name: Buster Shot

passive.description: Warwick's basic attacks deal bonus magic damage. If Warwick is below 50% health, he heals the same amount. If Warwick is below 25% health, this healing triples.
passive.name: Eternal Hunger

spells.description: Warwick lunges forward and bites his target, dealing damage based on their maximum health and healing for damage dealt.
spells.name: Jaws of the Beast

spells.description: Warwick senses enemies below 50% health, gaining Move Speed toward and attack speed against them. When they fall below 20% health, he frenzies and these bonuses triple.
spells.name: Blood Hunt

spells.description: Warwick gains damage reduction for 2.5 seconds. At the end, or if re-activated, he howls, causing nearby enemies to flee for 1 second.
spells.name: Primal Howl

spells.description: Warwick leaps in a direction (scaling with his bonus Move Speed), suppressing the first champion he collides with for 1.5 seconds.
spells.name: Infinite Duress

passive.description: Nunu increases the attack speed and Move Speed of Willump and a nearby ally, and causes Willump's basic attacks to damage enemies around the target.
passive.name: Call of the Freljord

spells.description: Willump takes a bite out of a minion, monster, or enemy champion, dealing damage and healing himself.
spells.name: Consume

spells.description: Willump creates a snowball that grows in size and speed as he rolls it.  The snowball damages and knocks up enemies.
spells.name: Biggest Snowball Ever!

spells.description: Nunu throws multiple snowballs that damage enemies.  When he's finished, Willump roots any champions or large monsters that were hit by a snowball.
spells.name: Snowball Barrage

spells.description: Nunu & Willump create a powerful blizzard in an area that slows enemies and deals massive damage at the end.
spells.name: Absolute Zero

passive.description: Miss Fortune deals bonus physical damage whenever she basic attacks a new target.
passive.name: Love Tap

skins.featuresText:
• Four deadly guns with matching Exo-Suits
  • New visual and sound effects for every Exo-Suit
  • Swap between weapons an unlimited number of times while at your base
  • Four exclusive icons which grant dynamic profile background
skins.name: Gun Goddess Miss Fortune

spells.description: Miss Fortune fires a bullet at an enemy, damaging them and a target behind them. Both strikes can also apply Love Tap.
spells.name: Double Up

spells.description: Miss Fortune passively gains Move Speed when not attacked. This ability can be activated to grant bonus Attack Speed for a short duration. While it's on cooldown, Love Taps reduce the remaining cooldown of Strut.
spells.name: Strut

spells.description: Miss Fortune reveals an area with a flurry of bullets, dealing waves of damage to opponents and slowing them.
spells.name: Make It Rain

spells.description: Miss Fortune channels a barrage of bullets into a cone in front of her, dealing large amounts of damage to enemies. Each wave of Bullet Time can critically strike
spells.name: Bullet Time

passive.description:
Ashe's attacks slow their target, causing her to deal increased damage to these targets.

Ashe's critical strikes deal no bonus damage but apply an empowered slow to the target.
passive.name: Frost Shot

spells.description: Ashe builds up Focus by attacking. At maximum Focus, Ashe can cast Ranger's Focus to consume all stacks of Focus, temporarily increasing her Attack Speed and transforming her basic attack into a powerful flurry attack for the duration.
spells.name: Ranger's Focus

spells.description: Ashe fires arrows in a cone for increased damage. Also applies Frost Shot.
spells.name: Volley

spells.description: Ashe sends her Hawk Spirit on a scouting mission anywhere on the map.
spells.name: Hawkshot

spells.description: Ashe fires a missile of ice in a straight line. If the arrow collides with an enemy Champion, it deals damage and stuns the Champion, stunning for longer the farther arrow has traveled. In addition, surrounding enemy units take damage and are slowed.
spells.name: Enchanted Crystal Arrow

passive.description: Tryndamere gains Fury for each attack, critical strike, and killing blow he makes. Fury passively increases his Critical Strike Chance and can be consumed with his Bloodlust spell.
passive.name: Battle Fury

spells.description: Tryndamere thrives on the thrills of combat, increasing his Attack Damage as he is more and more wounded. He can cast Bloodlust to consume his Fury and heal himself.
spells.name: Bloodlust

spells.description: Tryndamere lets out an insulting cry, decreasing surrounding champions' Attack Damage. Enemies with their backs turned to Tryndamere also have their Move Speed reduced.
spells.name: Mocking Shout

spells.description: Tryndamere slices toward a target unit, dealing damage to enemies in his path.
spells.name: Spinning Slash

spells.description: Tryndamere's lust for battle becomes so strong that he is unable to die, no matter how wounded he becomes.
spells.name: Undying Rage

passive.description: Jax's consecutive basic attacks continuously increase his Attack Speed.
passive.name: Relentless Assault

spells.description: Jax leaps toward a unit. If they are an enemy, he strikes them with his weapon.
spells.name: Leap Strike

spells.description: Jax charges his weapon with energy, causing his next attack to deal additional damage.
spells.name: Empower

spells.description: Jax's combat prowess allows him to dodge all incoming attacks for a short duration and then quickly counterattack, stunning all surrounding enemies.
spells.name: Counter Strike

spells.description: Every third consecutive attack deals additional Magic Damage. Additionally, Jax can activate this ability to deal damage around himself and strengthen his resolve, increasing his Armor and Magic Resist for a short duration.
spells.name: Grandmaster-at-Arms

passive.description: Morgana drains spirit from her enemies, healing as she deals damage to champions, large minions, and medium and larger jungler monsters.
passive.name: Soul Siphon

spells.description: Morgana binds an enemy in place with dark magic, forcing them to feel the pain they've caused and dealing magic damage.
spells.name: Dark Binding

spells.description: Morgana casts a cursed shadow on an area, damaging enemies who dare stand in her dark circle. They receive magic damage over time, which increases the lower health they are.
spells.name: Tormented Shadow

spells.description: Morgana anoints an ally with a protective barrier of starfire, which absorbs magical damage and disabling effects until it is broken.
spells.name: Black Shield

spells.description: Morgana unleashes the full force of her Celestial power as she unbinds her wings and hovers above the ground. She lashes chains of dark pain onto nearby enemy champions, gaining Move Speed towards them. The chains slow and deal initial damage and, after a delay, stun those who are unable to break them.
spells.name: Soul Shackles

passive.description: Zilean stores time as Experience and can grant it to his allies. When he has enough Experience to finish an ally's level up, he can right-click them to impart it. Zilean receives as much Experience as he gives.
passive.name: Time In A Bottle

spells.description: Tosses a bomb to target area that sticks to units that come near it (prioritizes Champions). It detonates after 3 seconds, dealing area of effect damage. If a Time Bomb is detonated early by another Time Bomb, it also stuns enemies.
spells.name: Time Bomb

spells.description: Zilean can prepare himself for future confrontations, reducing the cooldowns of his other basic abilities.
spells.name: Rewind

spells.description: Zilean bends time around any unit, decreasing an enemy's Move Speed or increasing an ally's Move Speed for a short time.
spells.name: Time Warp

spells.description: Zilean places a protective time rune on an allied champion, teleporting the champion back in time if they take lethal damage.
spells.name: Chronoshift

passive.description: Singed drafts off nearby champions, gaining a burst of Move Speed when passing them.
passive.name: Noxious Slipstream

spells.description: Leaves a trail of poison behind Singed, dealing damage to enemies caught in the path.
spells.name: Poison Trail

spells.description: Throws a vial of mega adhesive on the ground, slowing and grounding enemies who walk on it.
spells.name: Mega Adhesive

spells.description: Damages target enemy unit and flings them into the air behind Singed. If the target Singed flings lands in his Mega Adhesive, they are also rooted.
spells.name: Fling

spells.description: Singed drinks a potent brew of chemicals, granting him increased combat stats, and making his Poison Trail apply Grievous Wounds.
spells.name: Insanity Potion

passive.description: When out of combat, Evelynn enters Demon Shade. Demon Shade heals Evelynn when she is low on health and grants Camouflage after level 6.
passive.name: Demon Shade

spells.description: Evelynn strikes out with her Lasher, dealing damage to the first unit hit. Then, Evelynn can shoot a line of spikes at nearby foes up to 3 times.
spells.name: Hate Spike

spells.description: Evelynn curses her target, causing her next attack or spell after a delay to charm her target and reduce their magic resist.
spells.name: Allure

spells.description: Evelynn whips her target with her Lasher, dealing damage. She then gains Move Speed for a short duration.
spells.name: Whiplash

spells.description: Evelynn briefly goes untargetable and decimates the area in front of her before warping backwards a long distance.
spells.name: Last Caress

passive.description: Twitch's basic attacks infect the target, dealing true damage each second.
passive.name: Deadly Venom

spells.description:
Twitch becomes Camouflaged for a short duration and gains Move Speed. When leaving Camouflage, Twitch gains Attack Speed for a short duration.

When an enemy champion with Deadly Venom dies, Ambush's cooldown is reset.
spells.name: Ambush

spells.description: Twitch hurls a cask of venom that explodes in an area, slowing targets and applying deadly venom to the target.
spells.name: Venom Cask

spells.description: Twitch wreaks further havoc on poisoned enemies with a blast of his vile diseases.
spells.name: Contaminate

spells.description: Twitch unleashes the full power of his crossbow, shooting bolts over a great distance that pierce all enemies caught in their path.
spells.name: Spray and Pray

passive.description: Upon dying, Karthus enters a spirit form that allows him to continue casting spells.
passive.name: Death Defied

spells.description: Karthus unleashes a delayed blast at a location, dealing damage to nearby enemies. Deals increased damage to isolated enemies.
spells.name: Lay Waste

spells.description: Karthus creates a passable screen of leeching energy. Any enemy units that walk through the screen have their Move Speed and Magic Resist reduced for a period.
spells.name: Wall of Pain

spells.description: Karthus passively steals energy from his victims, gaining Mana on each kill. Alternatively, Karthus can surround himself in the souls of his prey, dealing damage to nearby enemies, but quickly draining his own Mana.
spells.name: Defile

spells.description: After channeling for 3 seconds, Karthus deals damage to all enemy champions.
spells.name: Requiem

passive.description: Whenever Cho'Gath kills a unit, he recovers Health and Mana. The values restored increase with Cho'Gath's level.
passive.name: Carnivore

spells.description: Ruptures the ground at target location, popping enemy units into the air, dealing damage and slowing them.
spells.name: Rupture

spells.description: Cho'Gath unleashes a terrible scream at enemies in a cone, dealing magic damage and Silencing enemies for a few seconds.
spells.name: Feral Scream

spells.description: Cho'Gath's attacks release deadly spikes, dealing damage and slowing all enemy units in front of him.
spells.name: Vorpal Spikes

spells.description: Devours an enemy unit, dealing a high amount of true damage. If the target is killed, Cho'Gath grows, gaining maximum Health.
spells.name: Feast

passive.description: Amumu's basic attacks <font color='#9b0f5f'>Curse</font> his enemies, causing them to take bonus true damage from incoming magic damage.
passive.name: Cursed Touch

spells.description: Amumu tosses a sticky bandage at a target, stunning and damaging the target while he pulls himself to them.
spells.name: Bandage Toss

spells.description: Overcome by anguish, nearby enemies lose a percentage of their maximum Health each second and have their <font color='#9b0f5f'>Curses</font> refreshed.
spells.name: Despair

spells.description: Permanently reduces the physical damage Amumu would take. Amumu can unleash his rage, dealing damage to surrounding enemies. Each time Amumu is hit, the cooldown on Tantrum is reduced.
spells.name: Tantrum

spells.description: Amumu entangles surrounding enemy units in bandages, applying his <keywordMajor>Curse</keywordMajor>, damaging and stunning them.
spells.name: Curse of the Sad Mummy

passive.description: Rammus' basic attacks deal bonus magic damage, scaling with his Armor.
passive.name: Spiked Shell

spells.description: Rammus accelerates in a ball towards his enemies, dealing damage and slowing targets affected by the impact.
spells.name: Powerball

spells.description: Rammus goes into a defensive formation, vastly increasing his Armor and Magic Resistance, amplifying Spiked Shells' damage, and returning damage to enemies that basic attack him.
spells.name: Defensive Ball Curl

spells.description: Rammus taunts an enemy champion or monster into a reckless assault against him. Additionally, he gains increased Attack Speed for a short time, but this bonus is extended by having any of his other spells active.
spells.name: Frenzying Taunt

spells.description: Rammus hops into the air and slams down at a target area, dealing magic damage and slowing enemies. If cast while Rammus is in Powerball, Rammus knocks up enemies near the center as well.
spells.name: Soaring Slam

passive.description: Upon taking fatal damage, Anivia reverts to an egg and is reborn with full health.
passive.name: Rebirth

spells.description: Anivia brings her wings together and summons a sphere of ice that flies towards her opponents, chilling and damaging anyone in its path. When the sphere explodes it does moderate damage in a radius, stunning anyone in the area.
spells.name: Flash Frost

spells.description: Anivia condenses the moisture in the air into an impassable wall of ice to block all movement. The wall only lasts a short duration before it melts.
spells.name: Crystallize

spells.description: With a flap of her wings, Anivia blasts a freezing gust of wind at her target, dealing damage. If the target was recently hit by Flash Frost or damaged by a fully formed Glacial Storm, the damage they take is doubled.
spells.name: Frostbite

spells.description: Anivia summons a driving rain of ice and hail to damage her enemies and slow their advance.
spells.name: Glacial Storm

passive.description: Shaco's basic attacks and Two-Shiv Poison deal additional damage when striking from behind.
passive.name: Backstab

spells.description:
Shaco becomes Invisible and teleports to target location.

His first attack while Invisible is empowered, dealing bonus damage and critically striking if he attacks from behind.
spells.name: Deceive

spells.description: Shaco creates a hidden animated Jack-in-the-Box. When triggered, it will fear and attack nearby enemies.
spells.name: Jack In The Box

spells.description: Shaco's Shivs passively poison targets on hit, slowing their Move Speed. He can throw his Shivs to deal damage and poison the target. The thrown Shiv deals bonus damage if the target is below 30% health.
spells.name: Two-Shiv Poison

spells.description: Shaco creates an illusion of himself near him, which can attack nearby enemies (Deals reduced damage to turrets).  Upon death, it explodes, spawning three mini Jack in the Boxes and dealing damage to nearby enemies.
spells.name: Hallucinate

passive.description:
Dr. Mundo resists the first Immobilizing effect that hits him, instead losing Health and dropping a chemical cannister nearby. Dr. Mundo can pick it up by walking over it, restoring Health and reducing this Ability's Cooldown.

Dr. Mundo also has significantly increased Health regeneration.
passive.name: Goes Where He Pleases

spells.description: Dr. Mundo throws an infected bonesaw, dealing damage to the first enemy hit based on their current health and slowing them.
spells.name: Infected Bonesaw

spells.description: Dr. Mundo electrocutes himself, dealing persistent damage to nearby enemies and storing a portion of damage he takes. At the end of the duration or on Recast, Dr. Mundo deals a burst of damage to nearby enemies. If the burst hit an enemy, he heals a percentage of the stored damage.
spells.name: Heart Zapper

spells.description:
Passive - Dr. Mundo gains bonus Attack Damage, increasing based on his max Health.

Active - Dr. Mundo slams his “medical” bag into an enemy, dealing additional damage based on his missing Health. If the enemy dies they are swatted away, dealing damage to enemies they pass through.
spells.name: Blunt Force Trauma

spells.description: Dr. Mundo pumps himself with chemicals, instantly healing a percent of his missing Health. He then gains Move Speed and regenerates a portion of his maximum Health over a long duration.
spells.name: Maximum Dosage

passive.description:
Accelerando: Sona gains non-Ultimate ability haste permanently for her basic abilities as she uses her abilities well, up to a cap. Beyond that cap, further successful uses reduce her ultimate's remaining cooldown instead.

Power Chord: Every few spell casts, Sona's next attack will deal bonus magic damage in addition to an additional effect based on what basic Ability Sona last activated.
passive.name: Power Chord

skins.featuresText:
• Trio of music styles
  • Show-stopping dance moves
  • Light show of effects
  • Music sharing with teammates
  • Three exclusive icons which grant dynamic profile background
skins.name: DJ Sona

spells.description: Sona plays the Hymn of Valor, sends out bolts of sound, dealing magic damage to two nearby enemies, prioritizing champions and monsters. Sona gains a temporary aura that grants allies tagged by the zone bonus damage on their next attack against enemies.
spells.name: Hymn of Valor

spells.description: Sona plays the Aria of Perseverance, sending out protective melodies, healing Sona and a nearby wounded ally. Sona gains a temporary aura that grants allies tagged by the zone a temporary shield.
spells.name: Aria of Perseverance

spells.description: Sona plays the Song of Celerity, granting nearby allies bonus Move Speed. Sona gains a temporary aura that grants allied champions tagged by the zone bonus Move Speed.
spells.name: Song of Celerity

spells.description: Sona plays her ultimate chord, stunning enemy champions and forcing them to dance and dealing magic damage to them. Each rank reduces the base cooldown of Sona's basic abilities.
spells.name: Crescendo

passive.description: Kassadin takes reduced magic damage and ignores unit collision.
passive.name: Void Stone

spells.description: Kassadin fires an orb of void energy at a target, dealing damage and interrupting channels. The excess energy forms around himself, granting a temporary shield that absorbs magic damage.
spells.name: Null Sphere

spells.description: Passive: Kassadin's basic attacks deal bonus magic damage. Active: Kassadin's next basic attack deals significant bonus magic damage and restores Mana.
spells.name: Nether Blade

spells.description: Kassadin draws energy from spells cast in his vicinity. Upon charging up, Kassadin can use Force Pulse to damage and slow enemies in a cone in front of him.
spells.name: Force Pulse

spells.description: Kassadin teleports to a nearby location dealing damage to nearby enemy units. Multiple Riftwalks in a short period of time cost additional Mana but also deal additional damage.
spells.name: Riftwalk

passive.description: When Irelia strikes enemies with spells she gains stacking bonus Attack Speed. At maximum stacks she also gains bonus damage on hit.
passive.name: Ionian Fervor

spells.description: Irelia dashes forward to strike her target, healing herself. If the target is Marked or dies to Bladesurge, its cooldown refreshes.
spells.name: Bladesurge

spells.description: Irelia charges a strike that deals more damage as she charges. She takes reduced physical damage during the charge.
spells.name: Defiant Dance

spells.description: Irelia sends out two blades which converge on each other. Enemies caught in between are damaged, stunned and Marked.
spells.name: Flawless Duet

spells.description: Irelia fires a massive number of blades that explode outward upon hitting an enemy champion. Enemies hit by the blades are damaged and Marked. Afterwards the blades form a wall that will damage and slow enemies that walk through it.
spells.name: Vanguard's Edge

passive.description: Janna gains bonus Move Speed moving towards allied champions and nearby allied champions gain this bonus when moving toward her.
passive.name: Tailwind

spells.description: By creating a localized change in pressure and temperature, Janna is able to create a small storm that grows in size with time. She can activate the spell again to release the storm. On release this storm will fly towards the direction it was cast in, dealing damage and knocking away any enemies in its path.
spells.name: Howling Gale

spells.description: Janna summons an air elemental that passively increases her Move Speed and enables her to pass through units. She may also activate this ability to deal damage and slow an enemy's Move Speed. The passive is lost while this ability is on cooldown.
spells.name: Zephyr

spells.description: Janna conjures a defensive gale that shields an ally champion or turret from incoming damage and increases their Attack Damage.
spells.name: Eye Of The Storm

spells.description: Janna surrounds herself in a magical storm, throwing enemies back. After the storm has settled, soothing winds heal nearby allies while the ability is active.
spells.name: Monsoon

passive.description: Every few seconds, Gangplank's melee strike will set his opponent on fire.
passive.name: Trial by Fire

spells.description: Shoots target, plundering Gold for each enemy unit killed.
spells.name: Parrrley

spells.description: Eats citrus to cure crowd control effects and restore Health.
spells.name: Remove Scurvy

spells.description: Gangplank uncovers a powder keg at target location. If he attacks it, it explodes, spreading the attack's damage to enemies in the area, slowing them.
spells.name: Powder Keg

spells.description: Gangplank signals his ship to bombard an area, slowing and damaging enemies.
spells.name: Cannon Barrage

passive.description:
A percentage of Corki's basic attack damage is converted into magic damage.

Corki can occasionally retrieve The Package inside his base, granting him Move Speed and an empowered cast of Valkyrie.
passive.name: Hextech Munitions

spells.description: Corki fires a flash bomb at a target location, dealing magic damage to enemies in the area. This attack additionally reveals units in the area for a duration.
spells.name: Phosphorus Bomb

spells.description: Corki flies a short distance, dropping bombs that create a trail of fire that damages opponents who remain in it.
spells.name: Valkyrie

spells.description: Corki's gatling gun rapidly fires in a cone in front of him, dealing damage and reducing enemy Armor and Magic Resist.
spells.name: Gatling Gun

spells.description: Corki fires a missile toward his target location that explodes on impact, dealing damage to enemies in an area. Corki stores missiles over time, up to a maximum. Every 3rd missile fired will be a Big One, dealing extra damage.
spells.name: Missile Barrage

passive.description: Karma's damaging abilities will reduce the cooldown of Mantra.
passive.name: Gathering Fire

spells.description:
Karma sends forth a ball of spirit energy that explodes and deals damage upon hitting an enemy unit.

Mantra Bonus: In addition to the explosion, Mantra increases the destructive power of her Inner Flame, creating a cataclysm which deals damage after a short delay.
spells.name: Inner Flame

spells.description:
Karma creates a tether between herself and a targeted enemy, dealing damage and revealing them. If the tether is not broken, the enemy will be rooted and damaged again.

Mantra Bonus: Karma strengthens the link, healing herself and extending the root duration.
spells.name: Focused Resolve

spells.description:
Karma summons a protective shield that absorbs incoming damage and increases the Move Speed of the protected ally.

Mantra Bonus: Energy radiates out from her target, strengthening the initial shield and applying Inspire to nearby allied champions.
spells.name: Inspire

spells.description: Karma empowers her next ability to do an additional effect. Mantra is available at level 1 and does not require a skill point.
spells.name: Mantra

passive.description: Spellcasts empower Taric's next 2 basic attacks to deal bonus magic damage, reduce his spell cooldowns, and attack in quick succession.
passive.name: Bravado

skins.name: Armor of the Fifth Age Taric

spells.description: Heals nearby allied champions based on charges stored. Bravado-empowered attacks grant a charge of Starlight's Touch.
spells.name: Starlight's Touch

spells.description:
Passively increase the Armor of Taric and any allied champion with Bastion.

Actively shields an ally and grants them Bastion for as long as they remain near Taric. Taric's spells also cast off the ally with Bastion.
spells.name: Bastion

spells.description: Taric readies a beam of starlight that, after a brief delay, deals magic damage and stuns enemies.
spells.name: Dazzle

spells.description: Pulses cosmic energy onto nearby allied champions after a delay, making them invulnerable for a short duration.
spells.name: Cosmic Radiance

passive.description: Veigar is the greatest Evil to ever strike at the hearts of Runeterra - and he's only getting bigger! Striking an enemy Champion with a spell or scoring a takedown grants Veigar permanently increased Ability Power.
passive.name: Phenomenal Evil Power

spells.description: Veigar unleashes a bolt of dark energy that deals magic damage to the first two enemies hit. Units killed by this bolt grant Veigar some ability power permanently.
spells.name: Baleful Strike

spells.description: Veigar calls a great mass of dark matter to fall from the sky to the target location, dealing magic damage when it lands. Stacks of Phenomenal Evil reduce Dark Matter's cooldown.
spells.name: Dark Matter

spells.description: Veigar twists the edges of space, creating a cage that Stuns enemies that pass through.
spells.name: Event Horizon

spells.description: Blasts target enemy champion, dealing a large amount of magic damage, increasing based on the target's missing health.
spells.name: Primordial Burst

passive.description: When an enemy unit dies near Trundle, he heals for a percent of its maximum Health.
passive.name: King's Tribute

spells.description: Trundle bites his opponent, dealing damage, briefly slowing and sapping some of their Attack Damage.
spells.name: Chomp

spells.description: Trundle turns target location into his domain, gaining Attack Speed, Move Speed, and increased healing from all sources while on it.
spells.name: Frozen Domain

spells.description: Trundle creates an ice pillar at target location, becoming impassable terrain and slowing all nearby enemy units.
spells.name: Pillar of Ice

spells.description: Trundle immediately steals a percent of his target's Health, Armor and Magic Resistance. Over the next 4 seconds the amount of Health, Armor, and Magic Resistance stolen is doubled.
spells.name: Subjugate

passive.description: Swain's ravens collect Soul Fragments that heal him and permanently increase his maximum health.
passive.name: Ravenous Flock

spells.description: Swain unleashes several bolts of eldritch power that pierce through enemies. Enemies hit take more damage for each bolt they are struck by.
spells.name: Death's Hand

spells.description: Swain opens a demon eye that deals damage and slows enemies. Champions hit are revealed and also grant Swain a Soul Fragment.
spells.name: Vision of Empire

spells.description: Swain launches a wave of demonic power forward. It then returns to Swain and roots enemies it hits. Swain can then choose to pull all rooted champions closer. This ability has a shorter cooldown during Demonic Ascension.
spells.name: Nevermove

spells.description: Swain transforms into a demon and drains health from nearby enemy champions, minions, and neutral monsters. Swain can cast Demonflare to decimate and slow nearby enemies with a nova of soulfire. This form is indefinite as long as Swain drains enemy champions.
spells.name: Demonic Ascension

passive.description: Every few basic attacks, or against a target she has trapped or netted, Caitlyn will fire a headshot dealing bonus damage that scales with her critical strike chance. On trapped or netted targets, Caitlyn's Headshot attack range is doubled.
passive.name: Headshot

spells.description: Caitlyn revs up her rifle for 1 second to unleash a penetrating shot that deals physical damage (deals less damage to subsequent targets).
spells.name: Piltover Peacemaker

spells.description: Caitlyn sets a trap that, when sprung, reveals and immobilizes the enemy champion for 1.5 seconds, granting Caitlyn an empowered Headshot.
spells.name: Yordle Snap Trap

spells.description: Caitlyn fires a heavy net to slow her target. The recoil knocks Caitlyn back.
spells.name: 90 Caliber Net

spells.description: Caitlyn takes time to line up the perfect shot, dealing massive damage to a single target at a huge range. Enemy champions can intercept the bullet for their ally.
spells.name: Ace in the Hole

passive.description: Blitzcrank gains a shield based on their mana when dropping to low health.
passive.name: Mana Barrier

spells.description: Blitzcrank fires their right hand to grab an opponent on its path, dealing damage and dragging it back to them.
spells.name: Rocket Grab

spells.description: Blitzcrank super charges themself to get dramatically increased Move and Attack Speed. They are temporarily slowed after the effect ends.
spells.name: Overdrive

spells.description: Blitzcrank charges up their fist to make the next attack deal double damage and pop their target up in the air.
spells.name: Power Fist

spells.description: Enemies attacked by Blitzcrank are marked and take lightning damage after 1 second. Additionally, Blitzcrank can activate this ability to remove nearby enemies' shields, damage them, and silence them briefly.
spells.name: Static Field

passive.description: Malphite is shielded by a layer of rock which absorbs damage up to 10% of his maximum Health. If Malphite has not been hit for a few seconds, this effect recharges.
passive.name: Granite Shield

spells.description: Malphite sends a shard of the earth through the ground at his foe, dealing damage upon impact and stealing Move Speed for 3 seconds.
spells.name: Seismic Shard

spells.description: Malphite attacks with such force that it creates a sonic boom. For the next few seconds, his attacks create aftershocks in front of him.
spells.name: Thunderclap

spells.description: Malphite slams the ground, sending out a shockwave that deals magic damage based on his Armor and reduces the Attack Speed of enemies for a short duration.
spells.name: Ground Slam

spells.description: Malphite launches himself to a location at high speed, damaging enemies and knocking them into the air.
spells.name: Unstoppable Force

passive.description:
Whenever an enemy champion dies that Katarina has damaged recently, her remaining ability cooldowns are dramatically reduced.

If Katarina picks up a Dagger, she uses it to slash through all nearby enemies, dealing magic damage.
passive.name: Voracity

spells.description: Katarina throws a <font color='#FFF673'>Dagger</font> at the target that then bounces to nearby enemies before ricocheting onto the ground.
spells.name: Bouncing Blade

spells.description: Katarina gains a burst of Move Speed, tossing a <font color='#FFF673'>Dagger</font> into the air directly above herself.
spells.name: Preparation

spells.description: Katarina blinks to the target, striking it if its an enemy, or striking the nearest enemy otherwise.
spells.name: Shunpo

spells.description: Katarina becomes a flurry of blades, dealing massive magic damage while she channels to the 3 nearest enemy champions.
spells.name: Death Lotus

passive.description:
Every few seconds, Nocturne's next attack strikes surrounding enemies for bonus physical damage and heals himself.

Nocturne's basic attacks reduce this cooldown.
passive.name: Umbra Blades

spells.description: Nocturne throws a shadow blade that deals damage, leaves a Dusk Trail, and causes champions to leave a Dusk Trail. While on the trail, Nocturne can move through units and has increased Move Speed and Attack Damage.
spells.name: Duskbringer

spells.description: Nocturne empowers his blades, passively gaining Attack Speed. Activating Shroud of Darkness allows Nocturne to fade into the shadows, creating a magical barrier which blocks a single enemy ability and doubles his passive Attack Speed if successful.
spells.name: Shroud of Darkness

spells.description: Nocturne plants a nightmare into his target's mind, dealing damage each second and applying fear to the target if they do not get out of range by the end of the duration.
spells.name: Unspeakable Horror

spells.description: Nocturne reduces the sight radius of all enemy champions and removes their ally vision in the process. He can then launch himself at a nearby enemy champion.
spells.name: Paranoia

passive.description: Maokai's basic attack also heals him and deals additional damage on a moderate cooldown. Each time Maokai casts a spell or is struck by an enemy's spell, this cooldown is reduced.
passive.name: Sap Magic

spells.description: Maokai knocks back nearby enemies with a shockwave, dealing magic damage and slowing them.
spells.name: Bramble Smash

spells.description: Maokai contorts into a mass of moving roots, becoming untargetable and dashing to the target. Upon arrival, he roots the target.
spells.name: Twisted Advance

spells.description: Maokai flings a sapling to the target area to stand guard. More effective in brush.
spells.name: Sapling Toss

spells.description: Maokai summons a colossal wall of brambles and thorns that slowly advances forwards, damaging and rooting any enemies in the path.
spells.name: Nature's Grasp

passive.description: Renekton's attacks generate Fury, increased when he is low on life. This Fury can empower his abilities with bonus effects.
passive.name: Reign of Anger

spells.description: Renekton swings his blade, dealing moderate physical damage to all targets around him, and heals for a small portion of the damage dealt. If he has more than 50 Fury, his damage and heal are increased.
spells.name: Cull the Meek

spells.description: Renekton slashes his target twice, dealing moderate physical damage and stuns them for 0.75 seconds. If Renekton has more than 50 Fury, he slashes his target three times, destroying damage shields on the target, dealing high physical damage, and stunning them for 1.5 seconds.
spells.name: Ruthless Predator

spells.description: Renekton dashes, dealing damage to units along the way. Empowered, Renekton deals bonus damage and reduces the Armor of units hit.
spells.name: Slice and Dice

spells.description: Renekton transforms into the Tyrant form, gaining bonus Health and dealing damage to enemies around him. While in this form, Renekton gains Fury periodically.
spells.name: Dominus

passive.description: Jarvan's first basic attack on an enemy deals bonus physical damage based on their current Health. This effect cannot occur again on the same enemy for a few seconds.
passive.name: Martial Cadence

spells.description: Jarvan IV extends his lance, dealing physical damage and lowering the Armor of enemies in its path. Additionally, this will pull Jarvan to his Demacian Standard, knocking up enemies in his path.
spells.name: Dragon Strike

spells.description: Jarvan IV calls upon the ancient kings of Demacia to shield him from harm and slow surrounding enemies.
spells.name: Golden Aegis

spells.description: Jarvan IV carries the pride of Demacia, passively granting him bonus Attack Speed. Activating Demacian Standard allows Jarvan IV to place a Demacian flag that deals magic damage on impact and grants Attack Speed to nearby allied champions.
spells.name: Demacian Standard

spells.description: Jarvan IV heroically leaps into battle at a target with such force that he terraforms the surrounding area to create an arena around them. Nearby enemies are damaged at the moment of impact.
spells.name: Cataclysm

passive.description:
Human Form: When Elise's abilities hit an enemy, she gains a dormant Spiderling.

Spider Form: Basic attacks deal bonus magic damage and restore health to Elise.
passive.name: Spider Queen

spells.description:
Human Form: Deals damage based upon how high the target's Health is.

Spider Form: Lunges at an enemy and deals damage based upon how low their Health is.
spells.name: Neurotoxin / Venomous Bite

spells.description:
Human Form: Releases a venom-gorged Spiderling that explodes when it nears a target.

Spider Form: Elise and her Spiderlings gain Attack Speed.
spells.name: Volatile Spiderling / Skittering Frenzy

spells.description:
Human Form: Stuns the first enemy unit hit and reveals them if they are not stealthed.

Spider Form: Elise and her Spiderlings ascend into the air and then descend upon target enemy. After descending on an enemy target, Elise's bonus damage and healing from Spider Queen is increased.
spells.name: Cocoon / Rappel

spells.description: Transforms into a menacing spider, reducing her attack range in exchange for Move Speed, new abilities, and a Spiderling swarm that will attack her foes.
spells.name: Spider Form

passive.description: Orianna's Attacks deal additional magic damage. This damage increases the more Orianna Attacks the same target.
passive.name: Clockwork Windup

spells.description: Orianna commands her Ball to fire toward a target location, dealing magic damage to targets along the way (deals less damage to subsequent targets). Her Ball remains at the target location after.
spells.name: Command: Attack

spells.description: Orianna commands her Ball to release a pulse of energy, dealing magic damage around it. This leaves a field behind that speeds up allies and slows enemies.
spells.name: Command: Dissonance

spells.description: Orianna commands her Ball to attach to an allied champion, Shielding them and dealing magic damage to any enemies it passes through on the way. Additionally, the Ball grants additional Armor and Magic Resist to the champion it is attached to.
spells.name: Command: Protect

spells.description: Orianna commands her Ball to unleash a shockwave, dealing magic damage and launching nearby enemies towards the Ball after a short delay.
spells.name: Command: Shockwave

passive.description: Wukong gains stacking armor and max health regeneration while fighting champions and monsters.
passive.name: Stone Skin

spells.description: Wukong's next attack gains attack range, deals bonus damage, and reduces the target's armor for a few seconds.
spells.name: Crushing Blow

spells.description: Wukong becomes <font color='#91d7ee'>Invisible</font> and dashes in a direction, leaving behind a clone that will attack nearby enemies.
spells.name: Warrior Trickster

spells.description: Wukong dashes to a targeted enemy and sends out images to attack enemies near his target, dealing damage to each enemy struck.
spells.name: Nimbus Strike

spells.description:
Wukong's extends his staff and spins it around repeatedly, gaining Move Speed.

Enemies struck take damage and are knocked up.
spells.name: Cyclone

passive.description: Brand's spells light his targets ablaze, dealing damage over 4 seconds, stacking up to 3 times. If Brand kills an enemy while it is ablaze he regains mana. When Blaze reaches max stacks on a Champion or large monster, it becomes unstable. It detonates in 2 seconds, applying spell effects and dealing massive damage in an area around the victim.
passive.name: Blaze

spells.description: Brand launches a ball of fire forward that deals magic damage. If the target is ablaze, Sear will stun the target for 1.5 seconds.
spells.name: Sear

spells.description: After a short delay, Brand creates a Pillar of Flame at a target area, dealing magic damage to enemy units within the area. Units that are ablaze take an additional 25% damage.
spells.name: Pillar of Flame

spells.description: Brand conjures a powerful blast at his target that spreads to nearby enemies, dealing magic damage. If the target is ablaze, Conflagration's spread is doubled.
spells.name: Conflagration

spells.description: Brand unleashes a devastating torrent of fire that bounces up to 5 times off of Brand and nearby enemies, dealing magic damage to enemies each time bounce. Bounces prioritize stacking Blaze to max on Champions. If a target is ablaze, Pyroclasm will briefly slow them.
spells.name: Pyroclasm

passive.description: After Lee Sin uses an ability, his next 2 basic attacks gain Attack Speed and return Energy.
passive.name: Flurry

spells.description:
Sonic Wave: Lee Sin projects a discordant wave of sound to locate his enemies, dealing physical damage to the first enemy it encounters. If Sonic Wave hits, Lee Sin can cast Resonating Strike for the next 3 seconds.
Resonating Strike: Lee Sin dashes to the enemy hit by Sonic Wave, dealing physical damage based on the target's missing Health.
spells.name: Sonic Wave / Resonating Strike

spells.description:
Safeguard: Lee Sin rushes to target ally, shielding himself from damage. If the ally is a champion, they are also shielded. After using Safeguard, Lee Sin can cast Iron Will for the next 3 seconds.
Iron Will: Lee Sin's intense training allows him to thrive in battle. For 4 seconds, Lee Sin gains Life Steal and Spell Vamp.
spells.name: Safeguard / Iron Will

spells.description:
Tempest: Lee Sin smashes the ground, sending out a shockwave that deals magic damage and reveals enemy units hit. If Tempest hits an enemy, Lee Sin can cast cripple for the next 3 seconds.
Cripple: Lee Sin cripples nearby enemies damaged by Tempest, reducing their Move Speed for 4 seconds. Move Speed recovers gradually over the duration.
spells.name: Tempest / Cripple

spells.description: Lee Sin performs a powerful roundhouse kick launching his target back, dealing physical damage to the target and any enemies they collide with. Enemies the target collides with are knocked into the air for a short duration. This technique was taught to him by Jesse Perring, although Lee Sin does not kick players off the map.
spells.name: Dragon's Rage

passive.description: Vayne ruthlessly hunts evil-doers, gaining <speed>30 Move Speed</speed> when moving toward nearby enemy champions.
passive.name: Night Hunter

spells.description: Vayne tumbles, maneuvering to carefully place her next shot. Her next attack deals bonus damage.
spells.name: Tumble

spells.description: Vayne tips her bolts with a rare metal, toxic to evil things. The third consecutive attack or ability against the same target deals a percentage of the target's max health as bonus true damage.
spells.name: Silver Bolts

spells.description: Vayne draws a heavy crossbow from her back, and fires a huge bolt at her target, knocking them back and dealing damage. If they collide with terrain, they are impaled, dealing bonus damage and stunning them.
spells.name: Condemn

spells.description: Readying herself for an epic confrontation, Vayne gains increased Attack Damage, Invisibility during Tumble, reduced Tumble cooldown, and more bonus Move Speed from Night Hunter
spells.name: Final Hour

passive.description: Every spell Rumble casts gives him Heat. When he reaches 50% Heat he reaches Danger Zone, granting all his basic abilities bonus effects. When he reaches 100% Heat, he starts Overheating, gaining bonus Attack Speed and granting his basic attacks bonus damage, but making him unable to cast spells for a few seconds.
passive.name: Junkyard Titan

spells.description: Rumble torches opponents in front of him, dealing magic damage in a cone for 3 seconds. While in Danger Zone this damage is increased.
spells.name: Flamespitter

spells.description: Rumble pulls up a shield, protecting him from damage and granting him a quick burst of speed. While in Danger Zone, the shield strength and speed bonus is increased.
spells.name: Scrap Shield

spells.description: Rumble launches a harpoon, electrocuting his target with magic damage, slowing their Move Speed, and reducing their Magic Resist. Rumble can carry 2 harpoons at a time. While in Danger Zone the damage and slow percentage is increased.
spells.name: Electro Harpoon

spells.description: Rumble fires off a group of rockets, creating a wall of flames that damages and slows enemies.
spells.name: The Equalizer

passive.description: Cassiopeia gains Move Speed per level, but she cannot purchase Boots items.
passive.name: Serpentine Grace

spells.description: Cassiopeia blasts an area with Poison after a brief delay, granting her increased Move Speed if she hits an enemy champion.
spells.name: Noxious Blast

spells.description: Cassiopeia releases several clouds of poison, slowing, grounding, and lightly damaging enemies that pass through them. Grounded enemies cannot use Movement abilities.
spells.name: Miasma

spells.description: Cassiopeia lets loose an attack that deals increased damage to Poisoned targets and heals her for a percentage of the damage dealt. If the target dies from this attack, Cassiopeia regains Mana.
spells.name: Twin Fang

spells.description: Cassiopeia releases a swirl of magical energy from her eyes, stunning any enemies in front of her that are facing her and slowing any others with their back turned.
spells.name: Petrifying Gaze

passive.description: Skarner's presence causes crystals to spawn in set locations around the map. Crystals can be captured by either team by standing close to them. When near crystals his team owns, Skarner gains Move Speed, attack speed, and increased mana regeneration.
passive.name: Crystal Spires

spells.description: Skarner lashes out with his claws, dealing physical damage to all nearby enemies and charging himself with Crystal Energy for several seconds if a unit is struck. If he casts Crystal Slash again while powered by Crystal Energy, he deals bonus magic damage.
spells.name: Crystal Slash

spells.description: Skarner gains a shield and has increased Move Speed while the shield persists.
spells.name: Crystalline Exoskeleton

spells.description: Skarner summons a blast of crystalline energy which deals damage to enemies struck and slows them. Basic attacking these enemies within a short window will stun them.
spells.name: Fracture

spells.description: Skarner suppresses an enemy champion and deals damage to it. During this time, Skarner can move freely and will drag his helpless victim around with him. When the effect ends, the target will be dealt additional damage.
spells.name: Impale

passive.description: Gain Move Speed while near allied towers and turrets deployed by Heimerdinger.
passive.name: Hextech Affinity

spells.description: Heimerdinger lays down a rapid-fire cannon turret equipped with a secondary pass-through beam attack (turrets deal half damage to towers).
spells.name: H-28 G Evolution Turret

spells.description: Heimerdinger fires long-range rockets that converge on his cursor.
spells.name: Hextech Micro-Rockets

spells.description: Heimerdinger lobs a grenade at a location, dealing damage to enemy units, as well as stunning anyone directly hit and slowing surrounding units.
spells.name: CH-2 Electron Storm Grenade

spells.description: Heimerdinger invents an upgrade, causing his next spell to have increased effects.
spells.name: UPGRADE!!!

passive.description: Nasus drains his foe's spiritual energy, giving him bonus Life Steal.
passive.name: Soul Eater

spells.description: Nasus strikes his foe, dealing damage and increasing the power of his future Siphoning Strikes if he slays his target.
spells.name: Siphoning Strike

spells.description: Nasus ages an enemy champion, decelerating their Move Speed and Attack Speed over time.
spells.name: Wither

spells.description: Nasus unleashes a spirit flame at a location, dealing damage and reducing the Armor of enemies who stand on it.
spells.name: Spirit Fire

spells.description: Nasus unleashes a mighty sandstorm that batters nearby enemies. While the storm rages, he gains increased Health, Attack Range, damages nearby enemies, has a reduced cooldown on Siphoning Strike, and gains bonus Armor and Magic Resistance.
spells.name: Fury of the Sands

passive.description:
Moving through brush increases Nidalee's Move Speed by 10% for 2 seconds, increased to 30% toward visible enemy champions within 1400 range.

Hitting champions or monsters with Javelin Toss or Bushwhack triggers a Hunt, granting True Sight of them for 4 seconds. During this time, Nidalee gains 10% Move Speed (increased to 30% toward the Hunted target) and her Takedown and Pounce are enhanced against them.
passive.name: Prowl

spells.description: In human form, Nidalee throws a spiked javelin at her target that gains damage as it flies.  As a cougar, her next attack will attempt to fatally wound her target, dealing more damage the less life they have.
spells.name: Javelin Toss / Takedown

spells.description: In human form, Nidalee lays a trap for unwary opponents that, when sprung, damages and reveals its target. As a cougar, she jumps in a direction, dealing damage in an area where she lands.
spells.name: Bushwhack / Pounce

spells.description: In human form, Nidalee channels the spirit of the cougar to heal her allies and imbue them with Attack Speed for a short duration. As a cougar, she claws in a direction, dealing damage to enemies in front of her.
spells.name: Primal Surge / Swipe

spells.description: Nidalee transforms into a cougar, gaining new abilities.
spells.name: Aspect Of The Cougar

passive.description: Udyr has four basic Abilities that swap between Stances and can Recast an Ability to renew it with additional benefits. Additionally, after using an Ability, Udyr's next two Attacks gain Attack Speed.
passive.name: Bridge Between

skins.featuresText:
• All-new spell effects and animations
  • Four model evolutions - one for each stance
  • Unique kill effects
  • Four exclusive icons which grant dynamic portrait background
skins.name: Spirit Guard Udyr

spells.description: Udyr gains attack speed and his next two attacks deal bonus physical damage. Recast: Gain even more attack speed, and the next two attacks call lightning to strike the target.
spells.name: Wilding Claw

spells.description: Udyr gains a shield and his next two attacks heal him. Recast: Gain an even bigger shield and heal based on max health over the next couple seconds.
spells.name: Iron Mantle

spells.description: Udyr gains movement speed and his first attack against each target will Stun them. Recast: Gain even more movement speed and immunity to immobilizing effects for a couple seconds.
spells.name: Blazing Stampede

spells.description: Udyr surrounds himself in a glacial storm, damaging and slowing nearby enemies. Recast: Empower and unleash the storm, causing it to track enemies and deal additional damage.
spells.name: Wingborne Storm

passive.description: Poppy throws her buckler that bounces off the target. Poppy can pick it up to gain a temporary shield.
passive.name: Iron Ambassador

spells.description: Poppy swings her hammer, dealing damage and creating a zone that will slow enemies and explode after a delay.
spells.name: Hammer Shock

spells.description: Poppy passively gains Armor and Magic Resist. This bonus increases when she is low on Health. Poppy can activate Steadfast Presence to gain Move Speed and stop enemy dashes around her. If a dash is stopped, the enemy is slowed and grounded.
spells.name: Steadfast Presence

spells.description: Poppy dashes to the target and pushes it back. If the target is pushed into a wall, it is stunned.
spells.name: Heroic Charge

spells.description: Poppy channels a hammer strike that knocks enemies very far away.
spells.name: Keeper's Verdict

passive.description: Gragas periodically heals upon using a skill.
passive.name: Happy Hour

spells.description: Gragas rolls his cask to a location, which can be activated to explode or will explode on its own after 4 seconds. The potency of the explosion increases over time. Enemies struck by the blast have their Move Speed slowed.
spells.name: Barrel Roll

spells.description: Gragas guzzles down brew from his cask for 1 second. After finishing, he becomes drunkenly empowered, dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies on his next basic attack and reducing damage received.
spells.name: Drunken Rage

spells.description: Gragas charges to a location and collides with the first enemy unit he comes across, dealing damage to all nearby enemy units and stunning them.
spells.name: Body Slam

spells.description: Gragas hurls his cask to a location, dealing damage and knocking back enemies caught in the blast radius.
spells.name: Explosive Cask

passive.description: Every few spells or attacks, Pantheon's next spell is empowered.
passive.name: Mortal Will

spells.description: Pantheon either thrusts his spear or throws his spear in the chosen direction.
spells.name: Comet Spear

spells.description: Pantheon dashes to a target, damaging and stunning them.
spells.name: Shield Vault

spells.description: Pantheon sets his shield, becoming invulnerable to damage from the front and striking repeatedly with his spear.
spells.name: Aegis Assault

spells.description: Pantheon composes himself and then leaps into the air, landing at a chosen location as a comet.
spells.name: Grand Starfall

passive.description: Ezreal gains increasing Attack Speed each time he successfully hits a spell, stacking up to 5 times.
passive.name: Rising Spell Force

skins.featuresText:
• All new spell effects and animations
  • Four stage evolving model
  • Pulsefire Ezreal and AI voices
  • Custom effects on a killing blow
  • Summoner icon
  • Summoner profile banner
skins.name: Pulsefire Ezreal

spells.description: Ezreal fires a damaging bolt of energy which reduces all of his cooldowns slightly if it strikes an enemy unit.
spells.name: Mystic Shot

spells.description: Ezreal fires an orb that sticks to the first champion or objective hit. If Ezreal hits an enemy with the orb, it detonates and deals damage.
spells.name: Essence Flux

spells.description: Ezreal teleports to a target nearby location and fires a homing bolt which strikes the nearest enemy unit. Prioritizes enemies stuck with Essence Flux.
spells.name: Arcane Shift

spells.description: Ezreal winds up before firing a powerful barrage of energy that deals massive damage to each unit it passes through (damage is reduced for minions and non-epic monsters).
spells.name: Trueshot Barrage

passive.description: Mordekaiser gains a powerful damage aura and Move Speed after landing 3 attacks or spells against champions or monsters.
passive.name: Darkness Rise

spells.description: Mordekaiser smashes the ground with his mace dealing damage to each enemy struck. Damage is increased when hitting a single enemy.
spells.name: Obliterate

spells.description: Mordekaiser stores damage he deals and takes to create a shield. He may consume the shield to heal.
spells.name: Indestructible

spells.description: Mordekaiser pulls all enemies in an area.
spells.name: Death's Grasp

spells.description: Mordekaiser drags his victim to a different dimension with him and steals a portion of their stats. If he kills them, he keeps the stats until the victim respawns.
spells.name: Realm of Death

passive.description: <font color='#FF9900'>The Cursed Horde:</font> Yorick can summon Mist Walkers to swarm and attack nearby enemies.
passive.name: Shepherd of Souls

spells.description: Yorick deals bonus damage on his next attack and heals himself. If the target dies a grave will be dug.
spells.name: Last Rites

spells.description: Yorick summons a destructible wall at target location that will block enemy movement.
spells.name: Dark Procession

spells.description: Yorick throws a globule of Black Mist that damages, slows and marks enemies.
spells.name: Mourning Mist

spells.description: Yorick summons the Maiden of the Mist that causes Yorick's attacks against the Maiden's target to deal bonus damage. The Maiden will also automatically raise Walkers from dead enemies.
spells.name: Eulogy of the Isles

passive.description: Dealing spell damage to a champion creates a ring of energy around them. Exiting that ring empowers Akali's next Attack with bonus range and damage.
passive.name: Assassin's Mark

spells.description: Akali throws out five kunai, dealing damage based on her bonus Attack Damage and Ability Power and slowing.
spells.name: Five Point Strike

spells.description: Akali drops a cover of smoke and briefly gains Move Speed. While inside the shroud, Akali becomes invisible and unable to be selected by enemy spells and attacks. Attacking or using abilities will briefly reveal her.
spells.name: Twilight Shroud

spells.description: Flip backward and fire a shuriken forward, dealing magic damage. The first enemy or smoke cloud hit is marked. Re-cast to dash to the marked target, dealing additional damage.
spells.name: Shuriken Flip

spells.description: Akali leaps in a direction, damaging enemies she strikes. Re-cast: Akali dashes in a direction, executing all enemies she strikes.
spells.name: Perfect Execution

passive.description: Kennen stuns enemies he hits 3 times with his abilities.
passive.name: Mark of the Storm

spells.description: Kennen throws a fast moving shuriken towards a location, causing damage and adding a Mark of the Storm to any opponent that it hits.
spells.name: Thundering Shuriken

spells.description: Kennen passively deals extra damage and adds a Mark of the Storm to his target every few attacks, and he can activate this ability to damage and add another Mark of the Storm to targets who are already marked.
spells.name: Electrical Surge

spells.description: Kennen morphs into a lightning form, enabling him to pass through units and apply a Mark of the Storm. Kennen gains Move Speed when entering this form, and attack speed when leaving it.
spells.name: Lightning Rush

spells.description: Kennen summons a storm that strikes at nearby enemy champions for magical damage.
spells.name: Slicing Maelstrom

passive.description: If Garen has not recently been struck by damage or enemy abilities, he regenerates a percentage of his total health each second.
passive.name: Perseverance

spells.description: Garen gains a burst of Move Speed, breaking free of all slows affecting him. His next attack strikes a vital area of his foe, dealing bonus damage and silencing them.
spells.name: Decisive Strike

spells.description: Garen passively increases his armor and magic resist by killing enemies. He may also activate this ability to give him a shield and tenacity for a brief moment followed by a lesser amount of damage reduction for a longer duration.
spells.name: Courage

spells.description: Garen rapidly spins his sword around his body, dealing physical damage to nearby enemies.
spells.name: Judgment

spells.description: Garen calls upon the might of Demacia to attempt to execute an enemy champion.
spells.name: Demacian Justice

passive.description: Damaging spells afflict enemies with Sunlight for 1.5 seconds. When allied Champions deal damage to those targets, they consume the Sunlight to deal additional magic damage.
passive.name: Sunlight

spells.description: Leona uses her shield to perform her next basic attack, dealing bonus magic damage and stunning the target.
spells.name: Shield of Daybreak

spells.description: Leona raises her shield to gain Damage Reduction, Armor, and Magic Resist. When the duration first ends, if there are nearby enemies, she will deal magic damage to them and prolong the duration of the effect.
spells.name: Eclipse

spells.description: Leona projects a solar image of her sword, dealing magic damage to all enemies in a line. When the image fades, the last enemy champion struck will be briefly immobilized and Leona will dash to them.
spells.name: Zenith Blade

spells.description: Leona calls down a beam of solar energy, dealing damage to enemies in an area. Enemies in the center of the area are stunned, while enemies on the outside are slowed.
spells.name: Solar Flare

passive.description: When he hasn't recently taken damage or been crowd controlled, Malzahar gains massive damage reduction and crowd control immunity, lingering for a short period after taking damage.
passive.name: Void Shift

spells.description: Malzahar opens up two portals to the Void. After a short delay, they fire projectiles that deal Magic Damage and silence enemy champions.
spells.name: Call of the Void

spells.description: Malzahar summons Voidlings to attack nearby enemies.
spells.name: Void Swarm

spells.description:
Malzahar infects his target's mind with cruel visions of their demise, dealing damage over time. Using Malzahar's other spells on the target will refresh the visions.

If the target dies while afflicted by the visions, they pass on to a nearby enemy unit and Malzahar gains Mana. Malzahar's Voidlings are attracted to affected units.
spells.name: Malefic Visions

spells.description: Malzahar channels the essence of the Void to suppress an enemy champion over a zone of damaging negative energy.
